[2026-04-05] Excellent! The fix is deployed. The issue was:

**What went wrong:**
- I added aggressive timeouts (25s for streaming, 28s for fetch) trying to prevent hanging
- These timeouts were way too short for generating 7-day trips
- Multi-day itineraries need more time to generate all the content
- Streaming responses don't hit Cloudflare's CPU time limit the same way

**What I fixed:**
- Removed the 25-second timeout from the streaming loop
- Removed the 28-second AbortController timeout from the fetch

